- <font color="#808080">OFFICER:</font> Yes, sir.

48:28.907 --> 48:31.659
We're gonna finish this thing
up today, ladies and germs.

48:31.826 --> 48:35.830
Victor's been out of circulation a while,
but there's still a residence in his name.

48:35.997 --> 48:37.707
