49:53.241 --> 49:55.451
Christ, what was his name?

49:56.786 --> 49:58.788
Spun him like a top.

49:58.955 --> 50:01.040
You know,
I mean, more like slow motion.

50:02.667 --> 50:04.585
I remember...

50:05.753 --> 50:07.088
