50:07.630 --> 50:10.216
Well, he died right there.

50:10.758 --> 50:12.427
Right there.

50:12.802 --> 50:14.929
Christ, what was
his fucking name?

50:27.817 --> 50:30.987
- <font color="#808080">OFFICER 1:</font> All rise.
