52:28.396 --> 52:30.439
Get up, you sack of shit.

52:35.236 --> 52:36.821
<font color="#D900D9">(COUGHING)</font>

52:36.988 --> 52:38.739
Oh, fuck me.

52:38.906 --> 52:43.077
Dicks, you'll wanna
come take a look at this.

52:45.872 --> 52:47.498
Dicks!

52:53.004 --> 52:54.213
