55:30.328 --> 55:33.831
Blood tests show a whole smorgasbord
of drugs in his system.

55:33.998 --> 55:35.249
Even an antibiotic...

55:35.416 --> 55:39.628
...which must've been administered
to keep the bed sores from infecting.

55:39.795 --> 55:43.758
Now, has he tried to speak
or communicate in any way?

55:43.924 --> 55:46.594
Even if his brain were not mush,
which it is...

55:46.761 --> 55:49.638
...he chewed off
his own tongue long ago.

55:51.140 --> 55:53.225
<font color="#808080">SOMERSET:</font>
Uh, Doc.

55:54.018 --> 55:57.271
Is there absolutely no chance
that he might survive?

55:57.772 --> 56:03.069
Detective, he'd die of shock right now if
you were to shine a flashlight in his eyes.

56:03.235 --> 56:06.781
He's experienced about as much pain
and suffering as anyone I've encountered.

56:06.947 --> 56:08.783
Give or take.

56:09.241 --> 56:12.244
And he still has hell
to look forward to.

56:12.495 --> 56:13.537
Good night.

56:13.704 --> 56:14.789
<font color="#D900D9">(PHONE RINGING)</font>

56:14.955 --> 56:17.541
<font color="#808080">MAN:</font> <font color="#D900D9">(ON RADIO)</font> <i>Tonight we bring you
