56:17.708 --> 56:20.711
<i>Featuring Sir Charles Thompson on
piano, Herb Pomeroy's trumpet...</i>

56:20.878 --> 56:25.424
<i>...Jimmy Woode, bass, Kenny Clarke, drums,
