56:25.591 --> 56:28.135
- Yeah?
- <i><font color="#808080">TRACY:</font> <font color="#D900D9">(OVER PHONE)</font> Hello, William?</i>

56:28.302 --> 56:32.014
- <i>It's Tracy.</i>
- Tracy?

56:32.181 --> 56:36.519
- Is everything all right?
- <font color="#808080">TRACY:</font> <i>Yeah, yes, everything's fine.</i>

56:36.685 --> 56:38.354
- Where's David?
- <font color="#808080">TRACY:</font> <i>He's just, uh...</i>

56:38.521 --> 56:40.898
<i>He's in the other room.
He's in the shower.</i>

56:41.065 --> 56:43.984
<i>Um, I'm sorry to
call you like this.</i>

56:44.151 --> 56:46.028
Oh, it's all right. Um...

56:46.487 --> 56:48.030
What can I do for you, Tracy?

56:49.573 --> 56:51.158
I, uh...

56:52.118 --> 56:53.661
Um, heh.

56:53.828 --> 56:55.704
I need someone to talk to.

56:55.871 --> 56:59.333
Do you think
you could meet me somewhere...

56:59.500 --> 57:01.001
...maybe tomorrow morning?

57:02.169 --> 57:04.338
I don't understand.

57:04.964 --> 57:08.050
<i>I feel stupid
calling, but, uh...</i>

57:09.135 --> 57:12.513
...you're the only person
that I know here.

57:12.680 --> 57:14.014
There's no one else.

57:14.598 --> 57:18.644
<i>If you can, just, uh,
give me a call, okay?</i>

57:18.811 --> 57:20.813
<i>I have to go now.</i>

57:21.355 --> 57:23.691
<i>- Well, good night.
- Good night.</i>

57:24.733 --> 57:26.861
<font color="#D900D9">(DIAL TONE)</font>

57:32.992 --> 57:36.829
<font color="#808080">TRACY:</font>
I mean, you know this city so well.

57:36.996 --> 57:40.958
You've been here so long.

57:41.876 --> 57:44.211
<font color="#808080">SOMERSET:</font>
It can be a hard place.

57:44.587 --> 57:47.047
I don't know why I
asked you to come.

57:48.883 --> 57:51.177
Why don't you talk
to him about it?

57:51.343 --> 57:53.012
Tell him how you feel.

57:54.221 --> 57:57.057
I can't. You know,
I can't be a burden.

57:57.224 --> 57:59.310
Especially now.

58:01.061 --> 58:03.063
I'll get used to things.

58:03.230 --> 58:05.191
You know? I think I just...

58:05.357 --> 58:09.653
I wanted to talk to someone who's
lived here for a long time and...

58:09.987 --> 58:16.202
I mean, upstate, you know, it's a
completely different environment.

58:18.871 --> 58:21.373
Did David tell you
that I teach fifth grade?

58:21.540 --> 58:23.209
Well, I did.

58:24.919 --> 58:27.004
Uh, he mentioned it.

58:30.049 --> 58:33.594
I've been going around,
you know, looking at schools.

58:34.261 --> 58:35.262
<font color="#D900D9">(SIGHS)</font>

58:35.429 --> 58:39.767
But the conditions
here are horrible.

58:41.060 --> 58:42.141
What about private schools?

58:42.269 --> 58:43.395
<font color="#D900D9">(SIGHS)</font>

58:45.272 --> 58:47.233
I don't know.

58:48.275 --> 58:51.445
Why don't you tell me
what's really bothering you, Tracy.

58:53.614 --> 58:56.242
David and I are
gonna have a baby.

59:00.704 --> 59:02.706
Oh, Tracy, I...

59:03.832 --> 59:05.709
I don't think I'm the, heh...

59:05.876 --> 59:08.170
I'm the one to talk
to about this.

59:08.337 --> 59:10.589
I hate this city.

59:14.385 --> 59:16.929
I had a relationship once.

59:17.304 --> 59:19.306
It was very much
like a marriage.

59:22.268 --> 59:24.311
We got pregnant.

59:25.104 --> 59:27.106
This was a long time ago.

59:31.819 --> 59:32.861
<font color="#D900D9">(SIGHS)</font>

59:33.028 --> 59:36.323
I remember getting up one morning
and going to work.

59:38.158 --> 59:42.871
Just another day like any other, except it
was the first day after I knew about...

59:43.455 --> 59:45.082
...the pregnancy.

59:46.208 --> 59:51.338
And I felt this fear for
the first time ever.

59:53.424 --> 59:57.761
I remember thinking how can I bring
a child into a world like this?

59:57.928 --> 01:00:02.182
How can...? How can a person grow up
with all this around them?

01:00:09.690 --> 01:00:12.109
I told her I didn't
want to have it.

01:00:14.111 --> 01:00:15.904
And over the next few weeks...

01:00:17.323 --> 01:00:19.325
...I wore her down.

01:00:21.702 --> 01:00:23.954
I wanna have children.

01:00:28.375 --> 01:00:30.711
I can tell you now that...

01:00:31.253 --> 01:00:33.380
I'm... I know, I mean...

01:00:33.547 --> 01:00:34.882
<font color="#D900D9">(CHUCKLES)</font>

01:00:35.591 --> 01:00:39.511
